<plot>Jack is a WWII paratrooper fighting on the front lines with the 502nd division deep within the war torn forests of France. After losing a buddy in his arms, Jack flees the war, finding a barn to hide in. Only in the barn is a German officer. Will Jack find humanity within the enemy, or will the night be silenced by the sound of the only rifle?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?083913</url></doc>
